name: Stained glass Aries unveils
description:
Watch the zodiac sign being revealed.   

Stained glass has always been a sign of happiness as it brings colorful light to dark places. It is playful, and just for that mixing it with a puzzle-like game makes it even more lively.   
With Ram as its symbol, Aries is the first zodiac sign among the twelve zodiac signs. People born from 21st March to 19th April are considered Aries natives. The element of Aries is 'Fire'. Every zodiac has its qualities based on its element. Aries is considered Hot and Dry as it has Fire element. The zodiac quality of Aries is considered 'Cardinal'. Being Cardinal sign, Aries natives are innovative and stubborn about what they want in their life.
